            . On the 26th of August, at five o'clock in the afternoon, I saw the prisoner come down stairs, and go out of the passage with a bundle under his arm. I did not see his face, but only his dress; he is dressed exactly the same now, and is the same height.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I bought the shirt.</p>
